{"word":"ὑπομονή","slug":"ὑπομονή","sections":[{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<b><el>ὑπομονή, ῆς, ἡ</el></b> [<el><a class=\"S\" href=\"S:ὑπομένω\">ὑπομένω</a></el>]<b><p class=\"pp1\"/>—<pp>1.</pp></b> ‘capacity for resolute continuance in a course of action’, <b>endurance, perseverance, steadfastness <a href='B:490 8:15'>Lk 8:15</a>; <a href='B:490 21:19'>21:19</a>; <a href='B:520 2:7'>Ro 2:7</a>; <a href='B:520 15:4'>15:4</a>; <a href='B:540 1:6'>2 Cor 1:6</a>; <a href='B:590 1:3'>1 Th 1:3</a>; <a href='B:600 3:5'>2 Th 3:5</a>; <a href='B:630 2:2'>Tit 2:2</a>; <a href='B:650 10:36'>Hb 10:36</a>; <a href='B:660 1:3'>Js 1:3f</a>; <a href='B:660 5:11'>5:11</a>; <a href='B:730 3:10'>Rv 3:10</a>.<p class=\"pp1\"/>—<pp>2.</pp></b> ‘persistence in awaiting realization of’ <a class=\"G\" href=\"S:✎ someth.\">someth.</a>, <b>expectation <a href='B:730 1:9'>Rv 1:9</a>.</b> <center id=\"nav_bottom\"> <a id=\"left_arrow\" href=\"S:ὑπόμνησις\">&ensp;&ensp;&ensp;&ensp;</a> <a id=\"bottom_home\" href=\"S:#1.Table of Contents\">&emsp;&emsp;</a> <a id=\"right_arrow\" href=\"S:ὑπονοέω\">&ensp;&ensp;&ensp;&ensp;</a> </center> "}]}